n standalone .exs scripts. | [FORMAT RULE] Only markdown code blocks allowed | [EXECUTION RULE] Code MUST run and produce correct output | [CONSISTENCY RULE] Project must match objective | [HEADER RULE - STRICT] You MUST start your entire response EXACTLY with this markdown block (do not print anything before it):
